            . I am an officer, and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was passing this window, and saw some bits of beef, which I thought would be better to buy for my children than tea, and next day I went in the shop and asked if she had any bits of beef - she said Yes; she then saw the mutton, and then said, "You have got meat enough, what do you want with more." I told her what I have told you now - she said, "This is our meat," and her daughter said, "Yes, it is."</p>
